    "body" : "<p><strong>Integers:</strong>  </p>\n\n<pre><code>int value = 100000; \nString.format(\"%,d\", value); // outputs 100,000\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Doubles:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>double value = 21403.3144d;\nString.format(\"%,.2f\", value); // outputs 21,403.31\n</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://sharkysoft.com/archive/printf/docs/javadocs/lava/clib/stdio/doc-files/specification.htm\" rel=\"noreferrer\">String.format is pretty powerful.</a></p>\n\n<p>-\nEdited per <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/users/1029912/psuzzi\">psuzzi</a> feedback.</p>\n"
