    "body" : "<p>can't you use a </p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.printf(\"%n%,d\",int name);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>The comma in the <code>printf</code> should add the commas into the <code>%d</code> inter.</p>\n\n<p>Not positive about it, but works for me.</p>\n"
